-- MERCEDES-BENZ (5 models)
('cm8x1a2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1','mercedes-benz-s-class-2024','MB001','WDDUG8CB7RA123456','Mercedes-Benz','S-Class','S 580 4MATIC',2024,145000,158000,12500,'Sedan','9-Speed Automatic','4.0L V8 Biturbo','Gasoline','AWD',4,5,'Black Obsidian','Macchiato Beige','The Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 580 represents the pinnacle of luxury sedans. Featuring a handcrafted 4.0L V8 biturbo engine producing 496 horsepower, this flagship delivers effortless performance with unmatched refinement. The interior showcases Nappa leather, active ambient lighting, and the latest MBUX hyperscreen.','Leather Seats,Panoramic Sunroof,Burmester Sound,MBUX Hyperscreen,Air Suspension,Massage Seats,Driver Assistance,360 Camera,Heated Steering,Wireless Charging','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618843479313-40f8afb4b4d8?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617531653520-4893f7bbf978?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617788138017-80ad40651399?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x1a2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j2','mercedes-benz-g63-amg-2023','MB002','W1NYC7HJ0PX123457','Mercedes-Benz','G-Class','G 63 AMG',2023,195000,210000,8500,'SUV','9-Speed Automatic','4.0L V8 Biturbo','Gasoline','AWD',5,5,'Designo Mystic Blue','Classic Red/Black','The Mercedes-AMG G 63 is an icon reborn. Its handcrafted AMG 4.0L V8 biturbo engine delivers 577 horsepower through a robust ladder-frame chassis. The legendary boxy design meets modern luxury with diamond-stitched leather and the latest technology.','AMG Performance,Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Burmester Sound,360 Camera,Adaptive Damping,Heated/Cooled Seats,Massage Seats,Trailering Package,Running Boards','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520031441872-265e4ff70366?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549399542-7e3f8b79c341?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563720360172-67b8f3dce741?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x1a2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j3','mercedes-benz-eqs-suv-2024','MB003','W1NKM4GB9RA123458','Mercedes-Benz','EQS SUV','580 4MATIC',2024,128000,142000,6200,'SUV','Single-Speed','Dual Electric Motors','Electric','AWD',5,7,'High-Tech Silver','Neva Grey/Black','The Mercedes-Benz EQS SUV 580 4MATIC combines zero-emission driving with S-Class luxury. With a 107.8 kWh battery providing exceptional range and dual motors producing 536 horsepower, this electric flagship redefines sustainable luxury.','Electric Range,Autopilot,MBUX Hyperscreen,Burmester Sound,Air Suspension,Massage Seats,Third Row,360 Camera,Wireless Charging,Heat Pump','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617788138017-80ad40651399?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606016159991-dfe4f2746ad5?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592198084033-aade902d1aae?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x1a2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j4','mercedes-benz-cle-coupe-2024','MB004','W1KAF4GB5RA123459','Mercedes-Benz','CLE','CLE 450 4MATIC',2024,72000,78000,4300,'Coupe','9-Speed Automatic','3.0L Inline-6 Turbo','Gasoline','AWD',2,4,'Patagonia Red','Saddle Brown','The Mercedes-Benz CLE Coupe combines elegant proportions with dynamic performance. The turbocharged inline-6 with mild hybrid assistance produces 375 horsepower, while the cabin features the latest MBUX interface and premium materials throughout.','Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Burmester Sound,MBUX,360 Camera,Heated Seats,Wireless Charging,Ambient Lighting,Heads-Up Display,Driver Assistance','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618843479313-40f8afb4b4d8?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549399542-7e3f8b79c341?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552519507-da3b142c6e3d?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x1a2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j5','mercedes-benz-gle-coupe-2023','MB005','W1N4M5GB6RA123460','Mercedes-Benz','GLE Coupe','AMG GLE 53',2023,95000,102000,15600,'SUV','9-Speed Automatic','3.0L Inline-6 Turbo','Gasoline','AWD',5,5,'Selenite Grey','Black/Red Stitching','The Mercedes-AMG GLE 53 Coupe merges SUV practicality with coupe styling. The AMG-enhanced 3.0L inline-6 produces 429 horsepower, while the sport-tuned air suspension and AMG Performance 4MATIC+ deliver exceptional handling and all-weather capability.','AMG Performance,Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Burmester Sound,Air Suspension,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance,Tow Package','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563720360172-67b8f3dce741?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606016159991-dfe4f2746ad5?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552519507-da3b142c6e3d?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

-- BMW (5 models)
,('cm8x2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k1','bmw-7-series-2024','BMW001','WBA33EJ09PCR12345','BMW','7 Series','740i xDrive',2024,110000,125000,8900,'Sedan','8-Speed Automatic','3.0L Inline-6 Turbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',4,5,'Frozen Deep Grey','Cognac Merino','The BMW 7 Series 740i xDrive represents the ultimate driving machine in luxury sedan form. The turbocharged inline-6 with 48V mild hybrid produces 375 horsepower. The interior features Merino leather, a curved display, and Executive Lounge seating.','Merino Leather,Panoramic Roof,Bowers & Wilkins Sound,Curved Display,Air Suspension,Massage Seats,Rear Entertainment,360 Camera,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555215695-3004980adade?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607853202273-797f1c22a38e?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523983388277-336a66bf9bcd?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2','bmw-x7-2023','BMW002','5UX23EU09P9C12346','BMW','X7','M60i xDrive',2023,115000,128000,11200,'SUV','8-Speed Automatic','4.4L V8 TwinPower', 'Gasoline','AWD',5,7,'Alpine White','Tartufo Merino','The BMW X7 M60i xDrive is the flagship of BMW SUVs. Its 4.4L V8 TwinPower turbo produces 523 horsepower, delivering commanding performance. The three-row interior offers first-class accommodations for seven with Merino leather and panoramic Sky Lounge LED roof.','Merino Leather,Panoramic Sky Lounge,Bowers & Wilkins Sound,Air Suspension,Third Row,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Massage Seats,Wireless Charging,Trailering Package','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556189250-72ba954e6790?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607853202273-797f1c22a38e?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523983388277-336a66bf9bcd?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k3','bmw-m4-competition-2024','BMW003','WBS43EJ09PCR12347','BMW','M4','Competition xDrive',2024,92000,98000,6700,'Coupe','8-Speed Automatic','3.0L Inline-6 TwinTurbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',2,4,'Isle of Man Green','Silverstone Merino','The BMW M4 Competition xDrive delivers motorsport-derived performance for the road. Its S58 3.0L twin-turbo inline-6 produces 503 horsepower, catapulting this coupe from 0-60 in just 3.4 seconds. The carbon fiber roof and aggressive styling announce its intent.','Merino Leather,Carbon Fiber Roof,Harman Kardon Sound,Head-Up Display,M Track Mode,Adaptive M Suspension,360 Camera,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance,M Sport Exhaust','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555215695-3004980adade?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607853202273-797f1c22a38e?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k4','bmw-ix-2024','BMW004','WBY43EJ09PCR12348','BMW','iX','xDrive50',2024,98000,108000,5400,'SUV','Single-Speed','Dual Electric Motors', 'Electric','AWD',5,5,'Storm Bay Metallic','Olive Leaf Merino','The BMW iX xDrive50 represents the future of BMW electric mobility. Dual motors produce 516 horsepower with a range of up to 307 miles. The minimalist interior features sustainable materials, a curved display, and iDrive 8 with natural language voice control.','Electric Range 307mi,Merino Leather,Panoramic Roof,Harman Kardon Sound,Air Suspension,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance,Self-Healing Grille','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606016159991-dfe4f2746ad5?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556189250-72ba954e6790?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x2b3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k5','bmw-z4-roadster-2023','BMW005','WBA43EJ09PCR12349','BMW','Z4','M40i',2023,68000,74000,9200,'Convertible','8-Speed Automatic','3.0L Inline-6 Turbo', 'Gasoline','RWD',2,2,'San Francisco Red','Black Vernasca','The BMW Z4 M40i Roadster delivers open-air exhilaration with precise handling. The turbocharged inline-6 produces 382 horsepower, while the soft-top retracts in just 10 seconds. Compact dimensions and perfect 50:50 weight distribution ensure sports car dynamics.','Vernasca Leather,Soft Top,Harman Kardon Sound,Head-Up Display,Adaptive M Suspension,360 Camera,Heated Seats,Wireless Charging,M Sport Brakes,Launch Control','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552519507-da3b142c6e3d?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523983388277-336a66bf9bcd?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

-- AUDI (5 models)
,('cm8x3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l1','audi-a8-l-2024','AUD001','WAU34BF29RN123450','Audi','A8 L','55 TFSI quattro',2024,102000,115000,7800,'Sedan','8-Speed Automatic','3.0L V6 Turbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',4,5,'Vesuvius Grey','Valcona Cognac','The Audi A8 L 55 TFSI quattro is a technological masterpiece disguised as a luxury sedan. The turbocharged V6 with mild hybrid produces 335 horsepower, while the predictive active suspension reads the road ahead. The rear seats offer foot massage and individual entertainment screens.','Valcona Leather,Panoramic Roof,Bang & Olufsen Sound,Predictive Suspension,Rear Massaging Seats,360 Camera,Head-Up Display,Wireless Charging,Night Vision,Driver Assistance','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603584173870-7f23fdae1b7a?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606016159991-dfe4f2746ad5?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l2','audi-q8-2023','AUD002','WA1AVAF19PD123451','Audi','Q8','RS Q8',2023,135000,148000,13400,'SUV','8-Speed Automatic','4.0L V8 TwinTurbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',5,5,'Dragon Orange','Black/Red Stitching','The Audi RS Q8 is the ultimate expression of performance SUV design. Its twin-turbo V8 produces 591 horsepower, making it one of the fastest SUVs on the planet. The coupe-like silhouette houses a luxurious cabin with RS-specific sport seats and carbon fiber trim.','RS Sport Seats,Panoramic Roof,Bang & Olufsen Sound,Air Suspension,RS Ceramic Brakes,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance,RS Exhaust','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603584173870-7f23fdae1b7a?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556189250-72ba954e6790?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3','audi-r8-v10-2023','AUD003','WUAANAF19PN123452','Audi','R8','V10 Performance quattro',2023,165000,185000,5600,'Coupe','7-Speed DCT','5.2L V10', 'Gasoline','AWD',2,2','Kemora Gray','Black Fine Nappa','The Audi R8 V10 Performance quattro represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated supercar engineering. Its 5.2L V10 produces 602 horsepower with a screaming 8,700 RPM redline. The carbon fiber monocoque and Quattro all-wheel drive deliver race car performance with daily usability.','Fine Nappa Leather,Carbon Fiber Monocoque,Bang & Olufsen Sound,Laser Headlights,Magnetic Ride,360 Camera,Heated Seats,Wireless Charging,Carbon Ceramic Brakes,Race Mode','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603584173870-7f23fdae1b7a?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552519507-da3b142c6e3d?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l4','audi-etron-gt-2024','AUD004','WA1LAAGF9RN123453','Audi','e-tron GT','RS',2024,125000,142000,4800,'Sedan','2-Speed Automatic','Dual Electric Motors', 'Electric','AWD',4,5,'Tactical Green','Black/Red Stitching','The Audi RS e-tron GT is an electric grand tourer that happens to be devastatingly quick. Dual motors produce 637 horsepower with a range of up to 249 miles. The swooping fastback design is as aerodynamic as it is beautiful, with matrix LED headlights and a spacious cabin.','Electric Range 249mi,Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Bang & Olufsen Sound,Air Suspension,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance,Matrix LEDs','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606016159991-dfe4f2746ad5?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603584173870-7f23fdae1b7a?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x3c4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l5','audi-q5-sportback-2024','AUD005','WA1A4AFY5RN123454','Audi','Q5 Sportback','SQ5',2024,72000,79000,10100,'SUV','8-Speed Automatic','3.0L V6 Turbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',5,5,'Navarra Blue','Okapi Brown','The Audi SQ5 Sportback combines coupe styling with SUV practicality. The turbocharged V6 produces 349 horsepower, while the sport-tuned suspension and quattro all-wheel drive deliver engaging handling. The sloped roofline adds style without significantly compromising rear headroom.','Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Bang & Olufsen Sound,Adaptive Air Suspension,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance,Tow Package,Virtual Cockpit','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603584173870-7f23fdae1b7a?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556189250-72ba954e6790?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

