,('cm8x4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3m1','porsche-911-turbo-s-2024','POR001','WP0AC2A99RS123455','Porsche','911','Turbo S',2024,245000,265000,3200,'Coupe','8-Speed PDK','3.7L Flat-6 TwinTurbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',2,4,'GT Silver Metallic','Black/Bordeaux Red','The Porsche 911 Turbo S is the ultimate everyday supercar. Its 3.7L twin-turbo flat-6 produces 640 horsepower, launching from 0-60 in 2.6 seconds. The rear-axle steering and active aerodynamics deliver track-capable handling with limousine comfort.','Leather Seats,Carbon Fiber Roof,Burmester Sound,Rear-Axle Steering,Active Aerodynamics,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Sport Chrono,PDCC','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544829099-f583c851cf65?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580274455191-1c62238fa333?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3m2','porsche-cayenne-turbo-2023','POR002','WP1AE2A29PL123456','Porsche','Cayenne','Turbo GT',2023,195000,210000,8700,'SUV','8-Speed PDK','4.0L V8 TwinTurbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',5,4,'Carmine Red','Black/Graphite Blue','The Porsche Cayenne Turbo GT is the fastest SUV around the Nurburgring. Its 4.0L V8 produces 631 horsepower with a titanium exhaust and carbon fiber roof. The lowered sport suspension and rear-axle steering transform this SUV into a genuine sports car.','Leather Seats,Carbon Fiber Roof,Burmester Sound,Titanium Exhaust,Rear-Axle Steering,Air Suspension,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Sport Chrono','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544829099-f583c851cf65?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580274455191-1c62238fa333?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3m3','porsche-taycan-turbo-s-2024','POR003','WP0AA2Y18RN123457','Porsche','Taycan','Turbo S',2024,195000,210000,4100,'Sedan','2-Speed Automatic','Dual Electric Motors', 'Electric','AWD',4,4,'Frozenberry Metallic','Black/Berry','The Porsche Taycan Turbo S redefines electric performance. Dual motors produce 750 horsepower with a 0-60 time of 2.6 seconds. The 800-volt architecture enables rapid charging, while the Porsche DNA ensures handling that no other EV can match.','Electric Range 222mi,Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Burmester Sound,Air Suspension,Rear-Axle Steering,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Sport Chrono','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606016159991-dfe4f2746ad5?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544829099-f583c851cf65?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580274455191-1c62238fa333?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3m4','porsche-718-cayman-gt4-2023','POR004','WP0AB2A81PK123458','Porsche','718 Cayman','GT4 RS',2023,165000,178000,2900,'Coupe','7-Speed PDK','4.0L Flat-6', 'Gasoline','RWD',2,2,'Shark Blue','Black/Race-Tex','The Porsche 718 Cayman GT4 RS is a mid-engine masterpiece. Its 4.0L naturally aspirated flat-6 produces 493 horsepower with a 9,000 RPM redline. The lightweight carbon fiber hood and swan-neck rear wing are derived from the 911 GT3, delivering genuine race car feel.','Race-Tex Seats,Carbon Fiber Hood,Swan-Neck Wing,Porsche Torque Vectoring,PCCB Brakes,Clubsport Package,360 Camera,Heated Seats,Wireless Charging,Sport Chrono','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580274455191-1c62238fa333?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544829099-f583c851cf65?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

('cm8x4d5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3m5','porsche-panamera-turbo-2024','POR005','WP0AE2A74RN123459','Porsche','Panamera','Turbo S Sport Turismo',2024,195000,210000,6800,'Wagon','8-Speed PDK','4.0L V8 TwinTurbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',5,4,'Mamba Green Metallic','Black/Crayon','The Porsche Panamera Turbo S Sport Turismo combines supercar performance with wagon practicality. Its twin-turbo V8 produces 620 horsepower, while the extended roofline provides exceptional cargo space. The rear seats fold flat for serious hauling capability without sacrificing Porsche dynamics.','Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Burmester Sound,Air Suspension,Rear-Axle Steering,360 Camera,Heated/Cooled Seats,Wireless Charging,Sport Chrono,PDCC','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544829099-f583c851cf65?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580274455191-1c62238fa333?w=800&q=80','available',0,NOW(),NOW()),

