,('cm8x5e6f7g8h9i0j1k2l3m4n1','lexus-ls-500-2024','LEX001','JTHB51F10R5123450','Lexus','LS','500 AWD',2024,92000,105000,9400,'Sedan','10-Speed Automatic','3.5L V6 TwinTurbo', 'Gasoline','AWD',4,5,'Manganese Luster','Kiriko Glass Black','The Lexus LS 500 AWD represents Japanese luxury at its finest. The twin-turbo V6 produces 416 horsepower with exceptional smoothness. The interior features hand-pleated door panels, Kiriko glass trim, and 28-way power seats with shiatsu massage.','Leather Seats,Panoramic Roof,Mark Levinson Sound,Air Suspension,Kiriko Glass,Rear Massaging Seats,360 Camera,Head-Up Display,Wireless Charging,Driver Assistance','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621939514649-280e2ee25f60?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800&q=80,https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552519507-da3b142c6e3d?w=800&q=80','available',1,NOW(),NOW()),

